  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Ireland supports 3 civil society organisations namely Caritas, Transparency International Zambia and Jesuit Centre for Theological Reflections (JCTR) under the delegated cooperation through GIZ. The support facilitates civil society to interface with relevant state actors in the formulation, implementation and monitoring of governance reform processes</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This was a delegated cooperation with GIZ which supported key CSOs ( Caritas,TIZ and JCTR) to advocate for improved transparency and accountability in Zambia. A saving of &#x20AC;60k was made on this budget line and was relinguished to HQ.</narrative>
  </description>
